ATSuccessStory v 0.1 build 5

Instructions:

- Place ATSuccessStory folder in your instance's Product folder

- Install it using QuickInstaller

- In portal_properties/site_properties add ATSuccessStory to
typesUseViewActionInListings property

- This Product includes a Portlet called portlet_success that
shows a random success story, and to work you have to create
a folder in your plone site with id=portlet-content and
inside another one with id=success-stories and place
inside all the success stories you want to be shown

